Theo Walcott took to Instagram to show off his birthday cake from his Arsenal team-mates ahead of their Champions League showdown with Monaco on Tuesday night.

Walcott turned 26 on Monday and Mesut Ozil was among those wishing the England international a happy birthday on social media.

While the perfect present may be qualification for the quarter-finals, Ozil wrote on Twitter: 'Happy 26th birthday to my friend @theowalcott #Stayhealthy #bestwishes #Gunners'

