Walcott, meanwhile, wrote on Instagram: 'Thank you to everyone for all the birthday messages today and a nice birthday cake surprise with the team.'

We know what he may be wishing for as Arsenal need to overturn a 3-1 deficit from their first leg in the Champions League last-16 tie at the Emirates.

It sees a return to Monaco for manager Arsene Wenger, who was in charge of them between 1987 and 1994.

